quran[27]{c,v,t}:
  37,127,"∆Āe njeddii mo, awa non, ko …ďe tawnoytee…ďe (ka lepte)."
  37,128,"Si wonaa jiyaa…ďe Alla la…ď…ďinaa…ďe …ďeen."
  37,129,"Min ngaccani mo mantoore, e sakkitii…ďe …ďen."
  37,130,""Kisal woni e dow Ilyaasiina'en"."
  37,131,"Ko wano nii Min njo…ďirta mo∆ī∆īim…ďe …ďeen."
  37,132,"KaŇčko, ko o jeyanoo…óo e jiyaa…ďe Amen gooŇč…óin…ďe …ďen."
  37,133,"Pellet, Luutu kadi, ko jiyanoo…óo e Nulaa…ďe …ďeen."
  37,134,"JaŇčto nde Min nda…óndunoo mo, kaŇčko e …ďeynguure makko nden fof,"
  37,135,"si wonaa nayeeja debba, tawaa…óo e luttunoo…ďe …ďeen,"
  37,136,"refti Min o∆ī∆īi heddii …ďe …ďeen."
  37,137,"Onon non, ho…óon ndewa e hoore-ma…ď…ďe, dawol mon."
  37,138,"e jemma. E on kaqqiltaa?"
  37,139,"Pellet, Yuunusa kadi, ko jiyanoo…óo e Nulaa…ďe …ďeen."
  37,140,"JaŇčto nde o dogirnoo ka laana hebbinaaka,"
  37,141,"o urbinii, o jiyaa e foolaa…ďe …ďeen."
  37,142,"Liinngii ngii mo…ói mo, ko o pelnii…óo."
  37,143,"Si wonaano tawde homo jeyanoo e subbunhinotoo…ďe …ďen,"
  37,144,"o √Īii…ďayno e reedu maggii, ha √Īalnde ummintinoytee."
  37,145,"Min mberlii mo ka ladde, ko o √Īawn…óo."
  37,146,"Min pu…óini e mayre, leggal buudi."
  37,147,"Min nuli mo e ujune teemeder yim…ďe, maa ko …ďuri."
  37,148,"∆Āe ngooŇč…óini, Min ndakmiti …ďe haa e dumunna."
  37,149,"La…ďndii …ďe:" E ko Joomi maa woodanta …ďi…ď…ďe rew…ďe, kam…ďe kan wor…ďe?"
  37,150,"Kaa Min tagir Maley'ikaaaji deww…óinaa…ói, hara ko …ďe seedii…ďe?""
  37,151,"Paamee, kam…ďe e pepindaale ma…ď…ďe …óen, hi…ďe mbi'a:"
  37,152,""Allah jibinii"; pellet, …ďe penat"
